Samsung:
1. Open Settings
2. Open Battery
3. Select Background usage limits
4. Select Deep sleeping apps
5. Select "+" upper right corner
6. Select every app, where you do not need a notification from
7. After selecting, press "Add"

Samsung:
1. Open Settings
2. Search for Adaptive Battery
3. Turn on
4. Go back and search for Adaptive Batterysavingmode
5. Turn on
